Great news!

Our team’s paper on active noise control, “Subband Active Noise Control with Pre-Trained Filters: A Low-Complexity Adaptive Combination Weight Algorithm,” has been accepted by Digital Signal Processing. The main contribution of this work lies in its low-complexity design, which significantly improves the practical applicability of the algorithm.
